node.text:
I would like to acknowledge the native Tongva peoples who are the original caretakers of Tovaangar (Los Angeles) and Puvungna (Long Beach). The skate shop resides on stolen Tongva land. 

Doug @steezyapache is a passionate skateboarder raising money to build a skate park on his tribe’s reservation in White River AZ. We did a fundraiser through our roller skate shop in January to support his efforts. And here are the results. 

WE RAISED $14,000!!!

THANK YOU ROLLER SKATING COMMUNITY! We did this together and I am so honored and humbled to be a part of these efforts. 

Shout out to my long time friends, fellow leader, coach and Native roller skater Elle Seven @squaregangster and her crew at Critical Medicine @skatingismedicine for partnering and guiding me in this project. It’s a true honor to work with you all and give back to the communities who have been torn apart for hundreds of years, and still today, by the colonizers of this land. 

Thank you to each and every person who supports the shop, supports small businesses, supports their community and supports the native peoples of America. 

#Repost @steezyapache 
・・・
Thank you to @pigeonskate @pigeonsrollerskateshop AND THE ENTIRE ROLLERSKATING COMMUNITY 🎯🛼
.
Let’s get this park built 🛠🪚
Special thanks to The Whiteriver Skate Scene, @skatingismedicine, @squaregangster, @indellica1

node.text: We wanted you all to see for yourselves how these skates SHINE in the dark! Deep purple in the day and an acid trip at night. It’s truly a one of a kind skate! The LAST BATCH of this rare model will be dropping on www.pigeonskates.com Monday Feb. 1st at Noon. This model has been discontinued due to the material scuffing too easy for the Moonlight brand’s liking during overseas transportation. However the scuffs are cosmetic and create no functional issues so these skates are perfect to roll out in. More details (and photos examples) on the product listing on our website!

PSA: Disco isn’t dead 🕺 And we want you to come see for yourself 😍

Enjoy this sneak peek of what’s in store for our @discoasis x @pigeonsrollerskateshop party happening Wednesday, July 28th!

Join us for this one-night-only event featuring:

• 3-Hour Exclusive Access
• Some of your favorite L.A. Skaters! 
• $250 Shop Gift Certificate Giveaway 
  for Best Dressed (Single + Duo)
• Music courtesy of @djwayned10 of the Sk8 Pop-Up!

Tap the link in our bio get your tickets & use code “PIGEON” to join the party! 🎉

The grass is greener where you water it 🌱😍 These homegrown customs were made just in time for the garden party happening @discoasis 🙌🏻

If you haven’t already, be sure to join us and some of SoCals grooviest skaters on July 28th for the Pigeon’s Skate Shop Party @discoasis 🙌🏻 Tap the link in our bio & use code ‘PIGEON’ for exclusive access 🎉

Also, DID YOU KNOW that on all other DiscOasis event nights you only get 30 minutes of rink time but during our Skate Shop Party you get all 3 hours?? 🛼 We can’t wait to skate the night away everyone!

Buckle up, buttercups 😉 We just added these NEW unique and amazing adjustable skate leashes with squeeze buckles (for extra ease 🙌🏻) by @gracexoriginals to the shop in 4 beautiful colorways!

We love supporting a female-owned, handmade, & sustainable brand 👏🏼 Each of these leashes are hand dyed and made of sustainable new/deadstock material...vintage Wrangler denim! 😍 Tap the photo to support & grab one for you!

*GIVEAWAY CLOSED* The Thankful Thursday Giveaway Series 🙌🏻

To show our gratitude for this uhh-mazing community, every Thursday we’ll be doing a flash 1-day giveaway to keep you rollin’ with the punches 😎

This Week: Impala Skateboard - LATIS 10” CRUISERBOARD

HOW TO ENTER:

* Like + Follow @pigeonsrollerskateshop
* Tag 2 friends you want to roll with in the comments 🤘🏽
* Share this post to your story 🙂 (be sure to tag us!)

Good luck & stay tuned for next week’s giveaway!

Giveaway entry period ends on July 16th, 2021 at 11:59 (pst). Each comment is a separate entry. Open to Domestic Entries (50 states + Puerto Rico). Retail value at ($134.95). Winner will be notified via Instagram Stories. This promotion is in no way sponsored, endorsed, administered by, or associated with Impala Skate or Instagram. If you receive a DM from asking for payment DO NOT REPLY, we will NEVER ask you for your credit card information (A.K.A. it’s the hackers trying to take advantage of our dope community)
